What does Shinichi want to tell me?

32
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:31,090
What could it be?

33
00:03:31,090 --> 00:03:33,490
A proposal, he's going to propose!

34
00:03:33,490 --> 00:03:35,290
What?

35
00:03:35,290 --> 00:03:38,790
I don't believe it, it can't be.

36
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:42,290
