49
00:04:25,690 --> 00:04:27,690
Are you sure about that?

50
00:04:27,690 --> 00:04:28,990
Yes.

51
00:04:28,990 --> 00:04:31,290
Tonight's party was in part,

52
00:04:31,290 --> 00:04:34,090
to celebrate the unveiling of our new company mascot,

53
00:04:34,090 --> 00:04:37,190
and the character was on stage all night.

54
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:40,390
We were shocked when we found out Mr Oba was inside it!

55
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,990
We really were.

56
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:43,390
I see.

57
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:46,190
So if he had another set of the same outfit,

58
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:48,090
