59
00:04:48,090 --> 00:04:49,890
with the powder burns on them.

60
00:04:49,890 --> 00:04:52,290
But he couldn't have.

61
00:04:52,290 --> 00:04:53,490
Before he change into his costume,

62
00:04:53,490 --> 00:04:57,290
Mr. Ooba handed us his jacket and slacks.

63
00:04:57,290 --> 00:04:58,490
But...

64
00:04:58,490 --> 00:05:00,290
He is suspicious, isn't he?

65
00:05:00,290 --> 00:05:01,990
