68
00:05:07,890 --> 00:05:10,490
Sure, it was funny at first.

69
00:05:10,490 --> 00:05:11,890
But that's the only thing he did.

70
00:05:11,890 --> 00:05:13,790
So after a while, it got pretty stale.

71
00:05:13,990 --> 00:05:15,390
Excuse me.

72
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:18,790
If you don't mind, may I take a look at that costume?

73
00:05:20,490 --> 00:05:22,090
So, this is it.

74
00:05:22,090 --> 00:05:24,590
The design's very surreal, isn't it?

75
00:05:24,590 --> 00:05:25,790
Isn't it adorable?

76
00:05:25,790 --> 00:05:28,290
Who was in charge of the party?

77
00:05:28,290 --> 00:05:29,590
Mr. Ooba.

78
00:05:32,790 --> 00:05:33,990
I've got it.

79
00:05:33,990 --> 00:05:35,990
So that's how he did it.

80
00:05:35,990 --> 00:05:38,590
So did you figure it out?

81
00:05:38,590 --> 00:05:40,390
Yes, most of it.

82
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:44,490
