83
00:05:44,490 --> 00:05:46,190
You must be kidding.

84
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:49,090
It's freezing, the cooler's on so high.

85
00:05:49,090 --> 00:05:51,690
Huh? Then, why am I perspiring so much?

86
00:06:01,290 --> 00:06:04,190
This can't be happening.

87
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:06,390
I don't believe it.

88
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:09,790
No, not now.

89
00:06:09,790 --> 00:06:12,390
Not here...

90
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:15,390
Not on this important day.

91
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:17,190
Darn it.

92
00:06:18,590 --> 00:06:20,790
Hey, are you all right?

93
00:06:20,790 --> 00:06:22,890
Kudo?

94
00:06:22,890 --> 00:06:24,290
Inspector Megure.

95
00:06:24,290 --> 00:06:27,290
We found no traces of powder on Mr. Ooba.

96
00:06:27,290 --> 00:06:28,590
I see.

97
00:06:28,590 --> 00:06:32,290
