101
00:06:36,590 --> 00:06:38,990
-Yes, sir. -Wait.

102
00:06:38,990 --> 00:06:41,490
There's no need for that.

103
00:06:41,490 --> 00:06:45,090
The killer is already among us.

104
00:06:45,090 --> 00:06:50,690
