105
00:06:52,290 --> 00:06:54,490
Hey! What's the meaning of this?

106
00:06:54,490 --> 00:06:56,590
You already checked me out.

107
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:58,990
They didn't find anything!

108
00:06:58,990 --> 00:07:03,490
So, why're you treating me Iike I'm the killer?

109
00:07:03,490 --> 00:07:05,890
Now, just calm down.

110
00:07:05,890 --> 00:07:09,890
You tell them that I couldn't have done it.

111
00:07:09,890 --> 00:07:12,790
Yes, I'll swear to it.

112
00:07:12,790 --> 00:07:15,890
Mr. Ooba was with me the whole time!

113
00:07:15,890 --> 00:07:19,790
Naturally, I wasn't with him when he changed into his costume,

114
00:07:19,790 --> 00:07:21,790
but the dressing room was locked.

115
00:07:21,790 --> 00:07:23,690
Besides, there were other people with him,

116
00:07:23,690 --> 00:07:25,590
so he couldn't have slipped out

117
00:07:25,590 --> 00:07:26,690
or switched places with someone else.

118
00:07:26,690 --> 00:07:29,690
Or are you implying that I'm lying?

119
00:07:29,690 --> 00:07:33,290
No, we don't suspect you of anything.

120
00:07:33,290 --> 00:07:38,690
You believe you were with Mr. Ooba through it all.

121
00:07:38,690 --> 00:07:42,690
Even while the murder was taking place.

122
00:07:42,690 --> 00:07:44,390
Wait a second.

123
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:48,490
Are you saying I helped a him kill my father?

124
00:07:48,490 --> 00:07:51,990
No, I'm saying that the murder took place near you.

125
00:07:51,990 --> 00:07:55,690
It's just that you didn't notice it.

126
00:07:55,690 --> 00:07:57,790
Because at the time it happened, you had your eyes closed

127
00:07:57,790 --> 00:07:59,990
and your back was facing the elevator

128
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:03,490
because you were kissing Mr. Ooba.

129
00:08:03,490 --> 00:08:05,590
They were kissing?

130
00:08:05,590 --> 00:08:08,090
Kissing? You mean...

131
00:08:08,090 --> 00:08:09,390
That's right.

132
00:08:11,290 --> 00:08:13,890
He cradled your head in his left arm like this,

133
00:08:13,890 --> 00:08:15,390
covering your ears

134
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:17,190
and while he was kissing you,

135
00:08:17,190 --> 00:08:20,190
he pushed the elevator call button.

136
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:21,890
And as soon as the door opened,

137
00:08:21,890 --> 00:08:25,590
your father was shot

138
00:08:25,590 --> 00:08:27,790
by Mr. Ooba.

139
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:32,490
But even if he covered her ears

140
